title: Mansions Discography
description:
Mansions LP (2007)
Mansions EP (2008)
New Best Friends (2009)
The EP Initiative (2009)
Manbox (2009)
Thyme Travel (2009)
Best of the Bees (2010)
Dig Up The Dead (2011)
Dig Up The Dead Acoustic (2011)
Fences/Mansions Split (2011)
The Deeper Hurts Reign (Daytrotter Session) (2011)
John Nolan/Mansions Split (2012)
Doom Loop (2013)
Audiotree Live (2014)*

Oh, and "Please Eat These Songs I Made For You", by "Bristopher Crowder", a pre-Mansions project. All songs on the album are covers.

I uploaded most of these as individual torrents but this is much easier. Not sure why I did this in the first place.

SEED TO HELP OUT ALL THE OTHER LOVERS OF OBSCURE MUSIC

*Audiotree Live does not include the film. TPB won't let you upload a file containing video into the "music" category. Sorry
